90 Sanidassanattika, Arūpāvacaraduka
Sanidassanattika, Arūpāvacaraduka
141.
336Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ arūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naarūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha…pe…  avigate cha.
337Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ naarūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paccayā nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanaarūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
